---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Button from "../components/ui/Button.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Me"
  description="About Nishanth's Blogs — engineering insights from a full-stack engineer building intelligent systems."
  includeNetwork={false}
>
  <div class="page-header" style="padding-top: 8rem; text-align: center;">
    <h1 class="page-title">Who Am I?</h1>
  </div>

  <section class="section about-content">
    <div class="section__inner content-wrapper">
      <p class="intro-text">
        I'm a full-stack engineer building intelligent, autonomous systems.
      </p>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2 class="content-heading">My Journey</h2>
        <ul class="styled-list">
          <li>
            Started with Python automation and developed numerous Django
            websites and APIs.
          </li>
          <li>
            Built serverless solutions leveraging AWS services like Lambda, API
            Gateway, SQS, DynamoDB, and EventBridge.
          </li>
          <li>
            Advanced into intelligent automation: exploring RAG systems,
            building agentic AI workflows, and understanding how modern LLMs can
            reason and act autonomously.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Today, I'm at the intersection of <strong>backend systems</strong> and <strong
            >autonomous AI</strong
          > by designing architectures where intelligent agents orchestrate complex
          workflows, integrate with external tools, and operate reliably in production.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2 class="content-heading">What I Build</h2>
        <ul class="styled-list">
          <li>
            <strong>Backend:</strong> Django APIs, database optimization, AWS infrastructure
            (Lambda, SQS, DynamoDB, EventBridge)
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Agentic AI:</strong> Autonomous agents with Claude, reasoning
            loops, tool orchestration, MCP integrations
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Workflow Automation:</strong> N8N pipelines, system integrations,
            event-driven architectures
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>RAG Systems:</strong> Semantic search, vector databases, knowledge
            retrieval at scale
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Sports & Data Engineering:</strong> Built specialized tools as a
            sports enthusiast, including a Duckworth-Lewis (DLS) calculator, IPL
            Playoff simulator, and a Kaggle data pipeline for T20I datasets
            leveraging AWS.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Development Setup:</strong> Building with Anthropic Claude, Google
            AI Studio, and modern AI tooling
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2 class="content-heading">Philosophy</h2>
        <p>
          I believe in learning in public. This blog documents the architecture
          decisions, debugging sessions, configuration patterns, and
          infrastructure choices that work. Not tutorials. Not theory. Just the
          documented path of someone building real systems and shipping them to
          production.
        </p>
        <p>
          My goal: Help other engineers navigate the shift toward intelligent,
          autonomous systems by sharing what I've learned along the way.
        </p>
      </div>

      <hr class="divider" />

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2 class="section__title">Expertise</h2>

        <div class="expertise-grid">
          <div class="expertise-item">
            <h3>Backend &amp; Infrastructure</h3>
            <p>
              Django, Python, PostgreSQL, AWS (Lambda, SQS, DynamoDB, S3,
              EventBridge), CI/CD, monitoring
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="expertise-item">
            <h3>AI &amp; Autonomous Systems</h3>
            <p>
              Claude (Anthropic), Agentic AI, ReAct prompting, function calling,
              tool orchestration, MCP
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="expertise-item">
            <h3>Intelligent Automation</h3>
            <p>
              N8N workflows, RAG systems, semantic search, vector databases, LLM
              integrations
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="expertise-item">
            <h3>Frontend &amp; Tools</h3>
            <p>
              React, Astro, Tailwind, command-line tools, Antigravity IDE
              (AI-assisted development)
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="expertise-item">
            <h3>DevOps &amp; Infrastructure</h3>
            <p>
              AWS deployment, serverless architecture, event-driven systems,
              monitoring, logging
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cta-container">
        <Button
          as="a"
          href="https://portfolio.nishanthm.com"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          variant="primary"
        >
          Read more about me &rarr;
        </Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .content-wrapper {
    max-width: 768px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .intro-text {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .content-block {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .content-block p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .content-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-accent-bright);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .styled-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .styled-list li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .styled-list li::before {
    content: "▹";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .styled-list li strong {
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .divider {
    border: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--color-border);
    margin: 4rem 0;
  }

  .section__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .expertise-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .expertise-item {
    background: var(--color-bg-elevated);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
  }

  .expertise-item h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-accent-bright);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .expertise-item p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .cta-container {
    margin-top: 4rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }
</style>
